        <h2>Eric Mogensen</h2>
        <div class="role">Design Innovation Lead</div>
        <p style="font-size:14px;color:var(--text-secondary);line-height:1.7;">Senior Designer at W.W. Grainger.<br>Founder, Octave Design Studio, LLC.</p>
        <div class="about-stats">
          <div class="about-stat"><span class="num blue">27+</span><span class="label">years in design</span></div>
          <div class="about-stat"><span class="num orange">13+</span><span class="label">years at Grainger</span></div>
